cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about video salient object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a new set of spatiotemporal deep features and a new spatiotemporal conditional random field, which are related to machine learning and deep learning. Therefore, cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper uses deep learning to improve the accuracy of video object segmentation, which is related to neural networks and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
